FuncDef: The display mpls rsvp-te command displays RSVP-TE configurations.
Examples: Hello interval: 3 sec                 Max Hello misses: 3
Path and Resv message refresh interval: 30 sec
Path and Resv message refresh retries count: 3
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
To view RSVP-TE signaling protocol configurations, run the display mpls rsvp-te command.
